'''Max Radio''' is a [[Sri Lanka]]n radio channel which broadcasts in [[Colombo]] and [[Kandy]]. It was launched on 10 September 2006. It is available on 90.6 FM in Colombo, and on 103.2 FM in Kandy. It is a Sinhala medium radio and operated by MGM Networks (Pvt) Ltd.

Naveen

